SIMPLE: unbark
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unbark
<hw>Un*bark"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>bark</ets> rind.]</ety> <def>To deprive of the
bark; to decorticate; to strip; <as>as, to <ex>unbark</ex> a
tree</as>.</def> <rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unbark</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unbark
<hw>Un*bark"</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref. <ets>un-</ets> +
<ets>bark</ets> the vessel.]</ety> <def>To cause to disembark; to
land.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Hakluyt.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unbarrel</ent>⟦br⟧
